            <h3 class="section-title">Introduction About SSTP, JPN Johor</h3>
            <p>Sektor Sumber Teknologi Pendidikan, Jabatan Pendidikan Negeri Johor (Educational Technology & Resources Sector, Johor State Education Department) is focused on:</p>
            <ul>
                <li class="list-item">Designing, implementing, and overseeing the development of educational technology materials based on Teaching and Learning (T&L) and disseminating them through various media to schools.</li>
                <li class="list-item">Planning, implementing, and providing guidance and expertise in educational technology to enhance innovation and creativity in T&L.</li>
