            <h3 class="section-title">Introduction to TV PSS</h3>
            <p>TV Pusat Sumber Sekolah (PSS) is a school program for students to showcase their talents in journalism, media, and hosting. The program aims to foster creativity and critical thinking among students by providing a platform for them to express themselves.</p>
            <p>The program uses a YouTube channel as its main broadcasting platform, giving students the opportunity to express their creativity and critical thinking skills.</p>
        </div>

        <div class="section">
            <h3 class="section-title">OFFICIAL/CIRCULAR LETTER</h3>
            <ul>
                <li class="list-item">Students are trained to operate a television channel.</li>
                <li class="list-item">They will cover broadcasting inside and outside the school as a learning activity.</li>
                <li class="list-item">The program helps students gain knowledge that will benefit their career path.</li>
                <li class="list-item">It fosters creativity and critical thinking.</li>
                <li class="list-item">Some students become hosts, journalists, screenwriters, and production crew members.</li>
                <li class="list-item">The knowledge gained will be applied in their learning.</li>
            </ul>
        </div>

